modName: JlynOX - Orchid The Flower Child Preset
summary: Orchid "The Flower Child" is a Racemenu Preset of another one of my "High Fantasy" characters  "Orchid".
descriptionHtml:
[b][color=#b4a7d6][center][size=6]Overview[/size][/center][/color][/b]
[list]
[*][color=#0000ff][size=4]Orchid [/size][/color][color=#8e7cc3][size=4]"[/size][/color][color=#0000ff][size=4]The Flower Child[/size][/color][color=#8e7cc3][size=4]"[/size][size=4] [/size][/color][color=#b4a7d6][size=4]is a [/size][/color][color=#00ffff][size=4]Racemenu[/size][/color][size=4] [/size][color=#b4a7d6][size=4]Preset of another one of my "High Fantasy" characters  "[/size][/color][color=#0000ff][size=4]Orchid[/size][/color][color=#b4a7d6][size=4]".[/size][/color]
[color=#b4a7d6][size=4]
[/size][/color][/list][color=#b4a7d6][size=4]
[/size][/color][list]
[*][color=#b4a7d6][size=4]She was made with a strong [/size][/color][color=#00ffff][size=4]Asian[/size][/color][color=#b4a7d6][size=4] [/size][/color][color=#00ffff][size=4]Imitation[/size][/color][color=#b4a7d6][size=4] along with some [/size][/color][color=#00ffff][size=4]Anime Stylization[/size][/color][color=#b4a7d6][size=4]. [/size][/color]
[/list][color=#b4a7d6][size=4]
[/size][/color][list]
[*][color=#b4a7d6][size=4]This is my second preset so far, i really enjoy making these but i hope you enjoy using them more. [/size][/color][color=#a64d79][size=4]Cheers[/size][/color][color=#b4a7d6][size=4]! [/size][/color]
[/list][color=#b4a7d6][size=4]
[/size][/color][list]
[*][color=#b4a7d6][size=4]Sorry [/size][/color][color=#00ffff][size=4]ECE[/size][/color][color=#b4a7d6][size=4] users I build this one up from [/size][/color][color=#00ffff][size=4]Racemenu.[/size][/color]
[/list]


[size=6][center][b][color=#b4a7d6]Requirements[/color][/b][/center]
[/size][size=4]
[list]
[*][color=#b4a7d6]KS Hairdos[/color]
[/list][color=#b4a7d6]
[/color][list]
[*][color=#b4a7d6]Mikan Eyes[/color]
[/list][color=#b4a7d6]
[/color][list]
[*][color=#b4a7d6]SG Eyebrows[/color]
[/list][color=#b4a7d6]
[/color][list]
[*][color=#b4a7d6]Fair Skin Complexion (All Options),  (I use Demoniac 8K FMS Specular Maps)[/color]
[/list][/size]
